.SH NOTES
.sp
.LP
The
.B NIS
makefile is only used when running the
.BR ypserv (1M)
server to provide
.B NIS
services. If these are being provided by the
.B NIS+
server running in
.B NIS
compatibility mode, see
.BR rpc.nisd (1M);
this makefile is not relevant.  See
.BR ypfiles (4)
for more details.
.sp
.LP
The Network Information Service (\fBNIS\fR) was formerly known as Sun
Yellow Pages
.RB ( YP ).
The functionality of the two remains the same.
